result_format: 4
投影项名称变更兼容控制
\N 兼容控制 (MySQL8.0 不支持)
select \N, null+1, Null, length(Null) from dual;
+------+--------+------+--------------+
| NULL | null+1 | NULL | length(Null) |
+------+--------+------+--------------+
| NULL |   NULL | NULL |         NULL |
+------+--------+------+--------------+
